{"tid":1933720,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"仲想有屋住？大家就必須肅清中資，整頓“港漂”","createTime":"2020-03-19T12:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T05:10:16.000Z","uid":304769,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6abefeef70ee6ba046dd97adfa6dcfcd2a14bc00","tid":1933720,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"黑警、狗官、奶共派唔洗我講，我開po係想講兩樣<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">會逐漸毀滅香港但無人留意的威脅</span></strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.中資</span></span></strong><br />\n從中國銀行支持送中，到交通銀行炒末日博士羅家聰，足以看到中資尤其國企的險惡本質，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他們的本質就是共產黨，只不過掛上不同招牌而已。而他們的任務就是將香港一切經濟利益、外匯、職位空缺全面送中，另外借助在商界影響力進行白色恐怖、噤聲、打壓香港人</span></strong>。而出賣香港人這一點，事實上早有大量先例，例如中聯辦書店旗下三中商政治審查書籍等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果大家對中共這個最大最危險敵人坐視不理，任由他們在香港做大，取得主要市場佔有率，真香港人將會面臨像澳門一樣既無野做（只有低級前線工作，而你上司係支那大學畢業講支那話既支那人）/無聲出（出聲即炒，唔跪即炒）既困境</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇我舊po<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.港漂</span></span></strong><br />\n一般人只留意到香港每日150低等蝗入侵香港。然而筆者認為&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;危害更大。因為150低等蝗普遍教育水平偏低，普遍只能做保安、潭仔阿姐等低下階層，對社會危害有限，大不了走水貨。而且他們普遍通過與香港人通婚進入，換言之有可能受感化而獲得良知，甚至變黃。<br />\n相反，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;普遍學歷偏高，能用流利蝗語和英語（香港留學後的IANG），故此他們較有機會爬到高位，甚至出任官員，對企業以及社會造成實質影響和破壞</span></strong>。其次，他們往往是一人進入香港後，再申請蝗配偶到港，再產下蝗卵。換言之，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">與香港聯繫甚低，難受普世價值感化，來港十年八年後仍然依賴微博等支那渠道獲得資訊甚為普遍，甚少&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;能在思維道德層面昇華到真香港人水平</span></strong>，卻更有機會爬到高層，故此&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;危害更大。<br />\n<br />\n原po：唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06fab141318d7949a09a0d87ecf840357afb2a13","tid":1933720,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c1f1bcd99e1cd565d66e4aca16e19c1a57aa53","tid":1933720,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T22:56:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58eeb143a1ff3b8b44e06c71c7cae12f850fc40e","tid":1933720,"uid":150992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d3fcbfb1b25ed47ddf80cf8d5eeed903460722e","tid":1933720,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"有屋住？依家係講緊有冇命"},{"pid":"5145466ec785a3a22cf62ce48e925df809cc76d1","tid":1933720,"uid":10056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"真 最緊要都係果班來港做野既大陸人 舉個例子個HR係香港大學畢業既大陸人 最後搞搞下成間公司一半以上都係依堆人 反而香港人仲少 依D應該係佢地既計劃黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0203c3f6ae8992f6260b19158555a3b89d33f5","tid":1933720,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5145466ec785a3a22cf62ce48e925df809cc76d1","tid":1933720,"uid":10056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"真 最緊要都係果班來港做野既大陸人 舉個例子個HR係香港大學畢業既大陸人 最後搞搞下成間公司一半以上都係依堆人 反而香港人仲少 依D應該係佢地既計劃黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"無錯，正是"},{"pid":"1ecc1de3c8d7a88d84518b3604d9abae963f5ffc","tid":1933720,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d3fcbfb1b25ed47ddf80cf8d5eeed903460722e","tid":1933720,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"有屋住？依家係講緊有冇命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"命、自由、錢、生活都重要"},{"pid":"299f4aa12b64b49800dd21df4f9ed45d6eb66f23","tid":1933720,"uid":299360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"同意 150個果種下一代接受左教育好多都好黃 呀爸呀媽低學歷又未咁大影響到香港人 但大學時果d nds 讀+工作七年就有身分證 果種最恐怖 而且人地係大陸十幾年再落黎香港 根本點都唔會係香港人 最後暗瓦底認同香港價值觀 但有起事上黎都係紅"},{"pid":"e41b5e647fc50cb548dfc59bd90fa3dd30e8786d","tid":1933720,"uid":212425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86190c0472e425bf69393343d2a8c001664e0c1","tid":1933720,"uid":9290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:16:22.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n冇人留意"},{"pid":"82ed062b78bee0c1b9f31034c0fc5de044830be3","tid":1933720,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"91c5b650ebc5cafc4c2aa2d14706dd7bafbb78f0","tid":1933720,"uid":262489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"上小紅書個個都買香港樓"},{"pid":"496821850b1797e59095d7a98b8cdd54da150088","tid":1933720,"uid":203161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"Agree and correct"},{"pid":"2902c72d4b610fb829c0c83932cc87539f6e552a","tid":1933720,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推，認真post冇人理。"},{"pid":"f0d330ad1714e172604c17ba62b99a500389f04f","tid":1933720,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2902c72d4b610fb829c0c83932cc87539f6e552a","tid":1933720,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推，認真post冇人理。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雞蟲巴"},{"pid":"d4c94426db44102e5f35b3fa1fabfc145c0c9777","tid":1933720,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"支持呢種觀點, 班友賺香港人錢一邊屌9香港人<br />\n中環都變左大灣區了"}]}